gamerules.gamerules2: 9 paylines, pays left to right and right to left
gamerules.wildRules: This symbol is WILD and substitutes for all symbols. Wild symbol appears in reels 2,3 and 4.
gamerules.wildRules2: The Wild symbol substitutes for all symbols. Any win containing a Wild has a multiplier of x2 applied to it.
gamerules.scatterRules: The Bitcoin Miner Symbol is a scatter. It is paid even when it does not appear on paylines and it should be in sequence.
